        "description": "Solver (ANSYS Fluent 2023R1) is a commercially validated, FDA-recognized CFD platform with documented version control, regression test suite, and release notes. Internal SQA records confirm all relevant modules (k-omega SST turbulence, user-defined hemolysis scalar transport) passed regression testing prior to this study."
