      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2023R1 is a commercially maintained solver subject to vendor SQA processes. Study-specific UDFs were version-controlled in a git repository with tagged release v2.3.1. Code review and unit tests for the hemolysis power-law UDF were documented in internal memo SQA-2024-07. All SQA activities meet or exceed MRL 2 gradation requirements."
